      "role": "user",
      "content": "the candles are all burned down to nothing... just like everything else. he's gone, and the silence in this house is heavier than the stone walls. i feel like i'm just a ghost already, wandering through these rooms where love used to live. i don't see the point in waiting for a morning that only brings more emptiness. i just want to let the shadows take me. i want to fade away into the night and never have to wake up to this ache again.",
